	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fasciculum literarum in vase <persName ref="p8126">Oporini</persName> inclusum nondum accepi; alias, quę ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749">Saxonia</placeName> fratres scriberent, tibi communicarem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quo in statu sint <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303">Magdeburgenses</placeName>, a <persName ref="p8171">Theodoro</persName> nostro petes.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam sint liberati prostratis hostibus impiis, ut nunquam revertantur.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510">Turca</placeName> nunc agat, vos scire non dubito.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="auto_name">Bresburgum</placeName> oppidum munitissimum cum arce cępit et iam habet tutissimum aditum in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l850">Austriam</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l619">Bavariam</placeName>, sicque orbis christianus evertetur brevi ab hostibus fidei; imo hostes evangelii deus per hanc virgam humiliabit, si digni sunt favore domini; nam non credo illos ad dominum reversuros post multas plagas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Episcopi duo, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7548">Moguntinus</persName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1028">Treverensis</placeName>, excepti prandio ab episcopo <placeName ref="l491">Argentoratensi</placeName> et inter prandendum varia locuti sunt de concilio.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l491">Argentoratensis</placeName> dixit: "Quid, si papales nullam admittent ecclesiae reformationem, imo vix confirmabunt Interim Caesareanum?"</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Respondit <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20531">Moguntinus</persName>: "Si non volunt ecclesiam reformare, in alium ordinem tam preces quam cantica redigere, tunc ego mox abiturus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Lutherani non veniant, quum a Caesare proscribantur passim in <placeName ref="l822" type="citizen_name">Germania</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ante annum consultarunt de eiiciendis concionatoribus; sed illud non sunt ausi exequi."</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1028">Treverensis</placeName> interrupit sermonem dicens: "Frustra insumimus magnos sumptus, et nihil fiet.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Turca disputabit cum Caesare, quem <persName type="auto_name">Gallus</persName> armavit" etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p4503">Ioachimus Camerarius</persName> electus a <persName ref="p18250">Mauricio</persName>, cui confessio fidei nova data est a doctis omnibus in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749">Saxonia</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l825">Dania</placeName>, <placeName type="auto_name">Bressia</placeName> et ab aliis civitatibus maritimis subscripta; nolunt enim se committere pontificiis.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De iis fusius fortassis tu nosti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsi tibi, ne mihi mittas Annotationes <persName ref="p8111">Petri Martyris</persName> in epistolam ad <placeName ref="l1855">Corinthios</placeName>, quum minoris possim<note type="margin">a.R.: possüm</note> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l28">Basileę</placeName> emere; verum si emisti, mitte ac rescribe, quos tu velis libros a me emptos, et diligenter id curabo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Brevi indicem librorum mittam novorum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui fit, quod vestri noluerunt comitia <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l21">Badena</placeName> adire?</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sitis fortes, obsecro vos per Christum, ac ne detis bello occasionem; nam pseudoevangelicis non est fidendum, et populi mores ita corrupti sunt, ut nihil sani sit sperandum ab illis.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">7. octobris 1551.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rescribe.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p1278">Gastius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dem eherwürdigen herren meyster <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name">Heinrich Bullinger</persName>, lütpriester zuͦ <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Zurich</placeName>, mynem günstigen herren zuͦ handen.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Zurich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
